To use the generic edit object:

#include <daemons.h>


To start an edit session:

EDIT_D->start_edit(string sData, object oCallbackObj, string sCallbackFunc);


where sData is a string to pre-stuff the edit buffer with, oCallbackObj is
the object which needs to be notified when the edit is done, and sCallbackFunc
is a function on that object of prototype:

void func(string sData, object oPlayer);

The edit daemon will call the callback object's callback function with the
data and the player doing the editing.

sData will be 0 if the player aborts the edit process.


Look in /open/OBJ/newsread.c for an example.

